cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper deals with wireless cellular networks and proposes network-assisted D2D schemes for supporting MTDs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and communication theory, which suggests cs.IT (Information Theory) as the second likely category. The paper also discusses interference cancellation and cognitive radio, which are related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SY (Systems and Control), respectively. Finally, the paper mentions the objective of maximizing the rate of broadband services for other devices, which could be related to cs.MM (Multimedia).
